</svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hzl1665703003956.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hzl1665703003956.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hzl1665703003956.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hzl1665703003956\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__nodebug_229762\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return focus to the application. For the character mode Debugger, stop the Debugger.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__topic_d74633e1_d74634e1_d74635e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__p_d74636e1_d74637e1_d74638e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nodebug</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__topic_d49162e1_d49163e1_d49164e1_d49165e1_d49166e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d319374e65\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__topic_d49167e1_d49168e1_d49169e1_d49170e1_d49171e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d319374e74\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__topic_d49172e1_d49173e1_d49174e1_d49175e1_d49176e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d319374e83\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__p_d74654e1_d74655e1_d74656e1\">In the interactive Debugger, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nodebug</span> statement returns focus to the application.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__p_d74657e1_d74658e1_d74659e1\">If you only want to activate the Debugger for a specific trigger, start the trigger with a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">debug</span> statement and terminate the trigger with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nodebug</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__p_d74660e1_d74661e1_d74662e1\">In the character mode Debugger, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nodebug</span> statement turns off the Debugger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__p_d74663e1_d74664e1_d74665e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">nop</code> debugger instruction has no effect on the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nodebug</span> statement. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">dump</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">xtrace</code> ProcScript debugger instructions stop their processing when they encounter a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nodebug</span> statement.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__section_swz_yhh_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d319374e129\">Example: Enabling and Disabling Debugging</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example enables debugging and starts an editing session,\n               then, when the edit session is completed, exits debug mode:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hzl1665703003956__pre_ah4_zhh_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n debug ; enter debug mode\n edit ; start editing session\n nodebug ; cancel debug mode when form is exited\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzg1665702766049.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Debugging in Character Mode</a><p>On a client running in character mode, the debug ProcScript statement causes a Debug command line to be displayed at the bottom of the screen.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/whw1665702766757.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>dump</a><p>Dump ProcScript instructions to the screen or message frame.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ygv1665702767461.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>nop</a><p>Skip the current statement without executing it.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjv1665702767767.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>xtrace</a><p>Start or stop the extended trace facility.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ayv1719391190685.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>debug</a><p>Start the Uniface Debugger.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528439\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528439\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "nodebug Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return focus to the application. For the character mode Debugger, stop the Debugger. nodebug Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description In the interactive Debugger, the nodebug statement returns focus to the application. If you only want to activate the Debugger for a specific trigger, start the trigger with a debug statement and terminate the trigger with nodebug . In the character mode Debugger, the nodebug statement turns off the Debugger. The nop debugger instruction has no effect on the nodebug statement. The dump and xtrace ProcScript debugger instructions stop their processing when they encounter a nodebug statement. Example: Enabling and Disabling Debugging The following example enables debugging and starts an editing session, then, when the edit session is completed, exits debug mode: operation exec debug ; enter debug mode edit ; start editing session nodebug ; cancel debug mode when form is exited end; exec Copy Related Links Debugging in Character Mode On a client running in character mode, the debug ProcScript statement causes a Debug command line to be displayed at the bottom of the screen. dump Dump ProcScript instructions to the screen or message frame. nop Skip the current statement without executing it. xtrace Start or stop the extended trace facility. debug Start the Uniface Debugger. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}